think weighed the meaning honestly rather than just approving: Sanskrit sala/shala means "hall/abode," the space one inhabits to see and use one's things -- a closer fit for a Landscape-parallel than Realidream was, and the gaushala (cow sanctuary) resonance ties directly to the project's own vegan/sanctuary mission. It honors the Vedic soul (Prakriti/Purusha) already behind Realidream's name.
